  "model_system_hint": "When answering research data questions: (1) check MODEL_GUIDE.json partition by topic, (2) prefer collection/{domain}/{partition}/ on GDrive as source of truth, (3) if action is hydrate, run collection_hydrate before analysis, (4) cite partition_id and target_drive_path."
